data.description: SUNSET VIEWS from this fantastic Jackson Pines Estates property! Enjoy your privacy with this corner lot as Bureau of Land Management land sits behind it.  Upon entering the driveway, you will find this home is perfect for entertaining. There is a large pool with plenty of patio area, perfect for a family get-together.  Walk inside the home, and you are greeted with the view from the balcony across. The kitchen has been recently remodeled with quartz countertops, double-oven, wine refrigerator, center island, and overlooks the spacious family room with vaulted ceilings.  In the primary suite, there is access to the balcony, a generously sized walk-in closet with custom shelving, 2 sinks, a jetted tub, and a shower.  There are 2 additional bedrooms and a bathroom on the main level.  On the lower level, there is a living room, a bedroom, and a bathroom with 2 sinks, with access to the yard.  Some additional amenities include a whole-house fan, cement roof, solar panels for a lower electric bill, finished 2-car garage with a quarter bathroom inside, indoor laundry room w/ closet, 2 sheds, and more.  Don't miss your opportunity to own this beautiful home.✨
